@startuml
title Online Quiz System State Transition Diagram

initial : User not logged in
state UserNotLoggedIn {}
state Teacher {}
state Student {}

UserNotLoggedIn --> RegisterOrLogin : Register or Login
RegisterOrLogin --> UserNotLoggedIn : Failed to register/login
RegisterOrLogin --> LoggedIn : Successfully registered/login

LoggedIn --> ContinueAsTeacher : Continue as teacher
LoggedIn --> ContinueAsStudent : Continue as student

ContinueAsTeacher --> CreateQuiz : Create a new quiz
CreateQuiz --> EditQuiz : Edit an existing quiz
EditQuiz --> SaveDraft : Save as draft
SaveDraft --> PostQuiz : Post for students
PostQuiz --> ViewResults : View quiz results

ContinueAsStudent --> SelectQuiz : Select a quiz after notification
SelectQuiz --> AnswerQuiz : Answer the selected quiz
AnswerQuiz --> SubmitQuiz : Submit the quiz
SubmitQuiz --> ViewResult : View result

ViewResults : Final state
ViewResult : Final state

@enduml
